5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rt\"><code>&lt;rt&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/rtc\"><code>&lt;rtc&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ruby\"><code>&lt;ruby&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>S\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/s\"><code>&lt;s&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\"><code>&lt;samp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\"><code>&lt;script&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/section\"><code>&lt;section&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\"><code>&lt;select&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\"><code>&lt;small&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Source\"><code>&lt;source&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"nonStdElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/spacer\"><code>&lt;spacer&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement deprecatedElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strike\"><code>&lt;strike&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\"><code>&lt;strong&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/style\"><code>&lt;style&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\"><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/summary\"><code>&lt;summary&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\"><code>&lt;sup&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>T\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/table\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tbody\"><code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/td\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"webcomp\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template\"><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\"><code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumo","title":"Resumo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>O elemento HTML <code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> representa uma posição no texto onde o navegador pode, opcionalmente, quebrar uma linha, embora suas regras de quebra de linha de outra forma não criar uma ruptura naquele local.</p>\n\n<p>Em UTF-8 páginas codificadas, <code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> se comporta como o <code>B L 200 </code><code>de tamanho zero ESPAÇO</code> ponto de código. Em particular, ele se comporta como um bidi Unicode BN ponto de código, o que significa que não tem efeito sobre bidi-encomenda: <code>&lt;div dir=rtl&gt; 123, &lt;wbr&gt; 456 &lt;/ div&gt;</code> exibe, quando não quebrado em duas linhas, <code>123.456</code> e Não <code>456,123</code> .</p>\n\n<p>Pela mesma razão, o <code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> elemento não introduzir um hífen no ponto de quebra de linha. Para fazer um hífen só aparecem no final de uma linha, use a entidade suave caractere hífen ( <code>&amp;shy;</code> ) em seu lugar.</p>\n\n<p>Este elemento foi implementado pela primeira vez no Internet Explorer 5.5 e foi oficialmente definido no HTML5.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"contexto_de_uso","title":"Contexto de uso","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Permitida conteúdo</td>\n   <td>Vazio</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Tag omissão</td>\n   <td>Este é um elemento vazio; ele deve ter uma marca de início, mas não deve ter uma tag de fechamento.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Elementos pai permitidas</td>\n   <td>Qualquer elemento que aceita <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\">conteúdo fraseado</a> .</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Documento normativo</td>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://dev.w3.org/html5/spec/text-level-semantics.html#the-wbr-element\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5, seção 4.6.24</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento só inclui os&nbsp; <a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\">atributos globais </a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_interface","title":"DOM interface","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento implementa o <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\">HTMLElement</a> interface.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://styleguide.yahoo.com/\" rel=\" noopener\">O Guia de Estilo Yahoo</a> </em> recomenda <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://styleguide.yahoo.com/editing/treat-abbreviations-capitalization-and-titles-consistently/website-names-and-addresses\" rel=\" noopener\">quebrar uma URL <em>antes de</em> pontuação</a> , para não deixar uma marca de pontuação no final da linha, o que o leitor pode confundir com o fim da URL.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>https://this<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.is<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.a<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.really<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.long<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.example<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>.com/With<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/deeper<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/level<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/pages<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/deeper<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/level<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/pages<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/deeper<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/level<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/pages<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/deeper<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/level<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/pages<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/deeper<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/level<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>wbr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>/pages<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Exemplo sample\" id=\"frame_exemplo\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr/_sample_.exemplo.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect2\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Cromo</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Ópera</th>\n   <th>Safári</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td>Unknown (3.0)</td>\n   <td>5.5</td>\n   <td>11,7</td>\n   <td>4.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Andróide</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>1.5</td>\n   <td>10.0 (10.0)</td>\n   <td>?</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Resumo","id":"resumo"},{"text":"Contexto de uso","id":"contexto_de_uso"},{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"DOM interface","id":"dom_interface"},{"text":"Exemplo","id":"exemplo"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"O elemento HTML <wbr> representa uma posição no texto onde o navegador pode, opcionalmente, quebrar uma linha, embora suas regras de quebra de linha de outra forma não criar uma ruptura naquele local.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<wbr>: The Line Break Opportunity element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<wbr>","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<wbr>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<wbr>","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<wbr>","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<wbr>","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<wbr>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/html/element/wbr","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/html/element/wbr/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Linguagem de Marcação de Hipertexto"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title